    <item>
      <title>KKR 联合首席执行官通过私募股权投资追随伯克希尔模式</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-11/kkr-co-ceos-following-berkshire-model-with-private-equity-bets</link>
      <description><![CDATA[KKR&amp;公司联席首席执行官乔·贝 (Joe Bae) 和斯科特·纳托尔 (Scott Nuttall) 借鉴伯克希尔哈撒韦公司 (Berkshire Hathaway Inc.) 的商业模式，在长期私募股权所有权和随之而来的股息上押下重注。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-11/kkr-co-ceos-following-berkshire-model-with-private-equity-bets</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Apr 2024 15:36:43 GMT</pubDate>
