    <item>
      <title>KKR 联合首席执行官谈增长目标和日本机遇</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-11/kkr-co-ceos-on-growth-target-opportunities-in-japan-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[KKR 联合首席执行官 Joe Bae 和 Scott Nuttall 讨论了该公司计划在五年内管理的资产规模至少达到 1 万亿美元。 Bae 和 Nuttall 在彭博电视台接受 Lisa Abramowicz 采访时还评论了 KKR 的战略持股、在日本的机遇以及在中国的投资。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-11/kkr-co-ceos-on-growth-target-opportunities-in-japan-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Apr 2024 15:24:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Destiny首席执行官称私人科技基金的模因式激增是一个“发现过程”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-11/destiny-ceo-calls-private-tech-fund-s-meme-like-surge-a-discovery-process</link>
      <description><![CDATA[本周，模因股票的狂热让一只封闭式基金变成了价值数十亿美元的庞然大物，使其摆脱了其私人持有股票的既定估值的束缚。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-11/destiny-ceo-calls-private-tech-fund-s-meme-like-surge-a-discovery-process</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Apr 2024 14:30:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>萨尔瓦多发行与国际货币基金组织和信用评级挂钩的新债券</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-11/el-salvador-returns-to-debt-market-with-marco-linked-bond</link>
      <description><![CDATA[萨尔瓦多将重返全球债务市场，如果政府未能赢得信用升级或与国际货币基金组织达成协议，该国将向投资者支付更高的利率。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-11/el-salvador-returns-to-debt-market-with-marco-linked-bond</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Apr 2024 13:25:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着买家财务压力的迹象出现，可可价格上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-11/cocoa-prices-climb-for-fifth-day-as-tight-supply-pain-lingers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[可可期货连续第五天上涨，预计未来几个月供应紧张将推动价格接近历史最高水平，随着压力迹象的出现，给贸易商和巧克力制造商带来财务障碍。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-11/cocoa-prices-climb-for-fifth-day-as-tight-supply-pain-lingers</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Apr 2024 12:04:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
